    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 &quot;Goo Go&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030820/extras/fb2a13cb5e17dfd2b215ca11fbc80707.poster.avif?t=1767802448\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030820/extras/fb2a13cb5e17dfd2b215ca11fbc80707.webm?t=1767802448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用三重跳跃和移动键来控制 Goo，克服障碍，不断攀升。这是一款非常具有挑战性的游戏，将考验你的技能、耐心，当然还有你的神经。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– 富有挑战性但并非不可能的游戏玩法。坚持和练习将帮助你达到顶峰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030820/extras/dd2e2b68b4626531aae2cd93baae4079.poster.avif?t=1767802448\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030820/extras/dd2e2b68b4626531aae2cd93baae4079.webm?t=1767802448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– 每一个障碍都是有意设计的，需要精确操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– 集中精力的游戏玩法，没有干扰元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– 你是永生的！但每一个错误或急躁都会让你回到起点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– 跳跃，跳跃，滑动，跌倒，然后重新开始。一遍又一遍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030820/extras/42045155560689a956b6bed435660638.poster.avif?t=1767802448\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030820/extras/42045155560689a956b6bed435660638.webm?t=1767802448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– 耐力和耐心的考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>开发者备注：</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏由一个人——我，独立制作。我受到了一些游戏的启发，比如 &quot;Getting Over It with Bennett Foddy&quot;, &quot;A Difficult Game About Climbing&quot; 和 &quot;Only Up!&quot; 的第一个版本。这些游戏是对 Jazzuo 的老游戏 &quot;Sexy Hiking&quot; 的致敬。我对这种游戏有复杂的感情：既恨又爱。它们燃烧神经元，但也带来成就的喜悦。我想为 &quot;Foddian Type&quot; 类型的游戏贡献一份力量，创造一些不仅仅是克隆，而是与众不同的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你好运和耐心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
